title: Asset Listing: Add $EURt on ETH v1
body:
Intro: This is a vote to list $EURt on ETH v1 with a collateral factor and collateral cap. 
Proposal: Via Listing Committee
Rational: List $EURt on ETH v1 market with collateral factor of 60% and collateral cap of $2M. CREAM and Tether are strategic partners and listing EURt will strengthen the partnership.  

For:  List $EURt on ETH v1 market with Collateral Factor: 60% and Collateral Cap: $2M.
Against:  Do nothing.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
